  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Open world, free exploration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game constructs a vast world inspired by the Classic of Mountains and Seas, featuring diverse terrains and hiding numerous natural treasures and secret realms. Scenes can be freely destroyed, and treasures may be hidden in any corner. Players must be vigilant against attacks from high-level exotic beasts during exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse gameplay, high energy throughout</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events and unexpected encounters are woven throughout the entire journey, allowing players to establish factions, seize territories, participate in martial arts competitions, bet on animal fights, and even experience the \"stone gambling\" gameplay. Additionally, interactions such as consignment and theft add strategic depth and fun to the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/6d675dca94ea646eafc0f8e75f8b3db7.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/6d675dca94ea646eafc0f8e75f8b3db7.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/6d675dca94ea646eafc0f8e75f8b3db7.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Evolution through devouring, character development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elevate your rank by devouring other exotic beasts, with the potential to evolve up to Tier 12, unlocking brand-new forms and skills. Allocate attribute points freely and craft your unique exotic beast with various natural treasures. Collect the Seven Dragon Balls to summon the hidden Tier 13 Ancient Dragon Ancestor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/39183c013ffc632d23569ca828a1ca0f.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/39183c013ffc632d23569ca828a1ca0f.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/39183c013ffc632d23569ca828a1ca0f.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engaging interaction, strategic manipulation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exotic beasts can mate and reproduce, and subdue lower-level exotic beasts as subordinates, commanding them to follow, attack, or stand by. They can also demand spirit stones, invite sparring, and engage in deep interactions that affect the battle landscape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c52ae244d3459eeb178e2f6192b078ee.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c52ae244d3459eeb178e2f6192b078ee.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c52ae244d3459eeb178e2f6192b078ee.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No cooling combat, talent awakening</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skills have no cooldown time, and can be released infinitely as long as there is sufficient true qi. The operation is more flexible. Exotic beasts can carry up to 8 skills, and after reaching level 12, they will awaken unique talents (such as the \"Nirvana Rebirth\" of the rosefinch), greatly enhancing their combat power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More gameplay updates continue, stay tuned...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/e6ac256dd598f5dcd8f5d551205680de.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Open world, free exploration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game constructs a vast world inspired by the Classic of Mountains and Seas, featuring diverse terrains and hiding numerous natural treasures and secret realms. Scenes can be freely destroyed, and treasures may be hidden in any corner. Players must be vigilant against attacks from high-level exotic beasts during exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.poster.avif?t=1769663501\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.webm?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2496920/extras/c3786bed57c90df421b289b3413d5ac5.mp4?t=1769663501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse gameplay, high energy throughout</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events and unexpected encounters are woven throughout the entire journey, allowing players to es